Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天召集大家不為別的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是為了和大家一起克服櫻花莊內的常識問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次櫻花莊會議的議題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於坐在這裡的椎名真白小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上讓人幫忙穿襪子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整好睡亂的頭髮就註定要遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:21.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:22.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.83,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 椎名 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上學的路上迷了路 到校的時候已經是第二節課了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:25.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名稍微有點那啥 是個無法正常生活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該輪流換班 制定一個能照顧她的體制…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了下 筆記本和不穿內褲讀起來挺像的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:41.23,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：筆記本（ノーパソ）　不穿內褲（ノーパン）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她父母只說了要人照顧的程度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才決定入住櫻花莊的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧？ 那老師你就要負起責任好好照顧她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下來了 這可是為了你而開的會議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:00:59.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好多…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很適合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 真白值日就決定是神田了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:08.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白值日？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.09,Other3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs34\c&H000000&\pos(640,328)}赤阪 龍之介：我可沒閑到有時間去參加那種凡塵瑣事的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.09,Other3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(346,426)}[ 龍之介退出了聊天室 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon也贊成哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員意見一致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:16.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:19.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 今晚要去護士紀子那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.91,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我可不能當作沒聽到 絕對不能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太奇怪了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.86,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花莊 議事錄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.86,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白值日就決定是神田空太了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.86,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.86,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會支持你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.86,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄•上井草美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.80,Title02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\pos(290,174)}#02 畫了畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲心菜 捲心菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:34.29,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公共場所清掃 廁所浴室的清掃 購物 炊事 倒垃圾 蜂巢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住！ 幸福會伴隨歎氣而飛走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收吧 來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很頭疼啊 “真白值日”什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我近期就準備離開櫻花莊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼… 那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼打扮啊！ 總之下面也穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲說不穿的話 空太會高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯啊 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人啊 你知道我要花多少工夫去教育椎名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.93,Other1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(690,80)\c&HEFD477&\3c&HFFFFFF&}模仿真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋說愛怎麼做怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 早餐都吃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點回房間去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備內衣都不穿就要去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲心菜怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早就去便利店好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁君 感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼了 突然有股惡寒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛都飛掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傷… 沙拉味要380円
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人份就是760円
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對錢包好傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太還沒好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 椎名小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃年輪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡就能被原諒的話 就不需要員警了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要付錢的 你的人生是怎麼過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫畫過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫畫過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等其他句子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.18,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還拿了一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說也付了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫椎名真白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年轉入美術科二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在住在櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起住在櫻花莊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們關係真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太是我第一個男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個第一次是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 椎名你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太是我的第一次真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好骯髒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 青山！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在英國都是和女生在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太是第一個和我要好的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些你早點說啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說？ 對剛才那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天絕對要買到炒飯麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繭的便當好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海 你知道空太在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又幹了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹 幹幹幹幹幹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 愉快的午餐時間卻只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人排斥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只買了一個麵包 只能用水來撐肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好堅強！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為椎名的關係伙食費才沒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師是椎名的看護人吧 快付款啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你的升學調查表還沒交來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移話題也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說椎名她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西隨便寫上飛行員不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是小學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:39.02,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術科 3年 上井草美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:39.02,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太耀眼了看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微學學人家上井草嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個菊花小的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:42.85,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個有野心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種是地球人無法模仿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話了 直接升學兩個字就能打發職員室了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是升學調查 看著你就感覺很有意義的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說一般是沒意義的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寫上“總之先升學”的學生 肯定都是為了發展而寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“總之”這個詞 有啤酒就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.83,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}注：とりあえずビール（總之先喝酒）是日本宴會裡的慣用句 意指宴會席上第一杯酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被完美地轉移話題了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒飯麵包到手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是強詞奪理…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前途嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個 又登上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上井草學姐和三鷹學長的採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對天才組合原來是青梅竹馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面說天才女高中生出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人看上去只是個變態 卻擁有很棒的才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厲害 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君 找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一個人就能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行 不在一起的話不知道你又會幹出什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 不准隨便吃別人賣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可愛的女孩是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有你能碰上這種好事 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:39.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰你個頭啊 那傢伙很奇怪的 很異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可愛程度的確很異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 總是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山完全給誤會了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾乃 平時那輛車呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去車檢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車檢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和心愛的寶貝暫時分離呢 真是難受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名小姐怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和英國的麗塔分開不會覺得難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空太在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在英國都是和女生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太是第一個和我要好的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在英國都是和女生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個 你在說什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太說要先把這個告訴你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 都是我自己一個人胡思亂想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要我怎麼面對神田君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 對不起 我好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是椎名同學對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太說沒付錢不能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來兩個年輪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名那傢伙有好好回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你來接我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛粘著我也沒什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮的捲心菜之路…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就有預感了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來得早是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的生日在房間裡等著的是用生奶油裝飾自己的美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請節哀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可為什麼會是捲心菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲的想法誰會懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是青梅竹馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說天才的想法對凡人是個謎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁學長要是凡人的話 那我算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:13:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先告辭…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼危險的東西要我一個人打開嗎 你還有良心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會爆炸的 所以沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是應該吧應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很傷眼 快點停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 仁真是害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都這麼出賣身體來給你慶祝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這次我要告辭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.53,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個捲心菜必須由工作人員美味地吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會幫我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是工作人員！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會吃的 你快點放棄吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不能磨蹭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的常識被侵蝕掉之前 要快點離開櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標並不是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的龍之介大人根據「程式設計員每天必須睡8個小時」這個理論
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在伴隨著美夢地休息中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 希望能陪龍之介大人一起睡的女僕發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼吵鬧的情況下還能做美夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名你回…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼想看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是空太的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很難為情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會難為情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾乃給的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年報了漫畫新人獎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿獎了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落選了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看過我的作品的綾乃 因為我畫得好就聯繫了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是編輯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是綾乃的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要從這裡開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纖細的感情表現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果覺得很難的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就試試過激點的描寫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才聯繫到男人的裸體嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟少女漫畫相對過激一點嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脫的話 空太也會脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 知道了 我脫 我脫總行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是內褲我不會脫的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲由我來脫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦子有問題吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺硬實厚重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳變快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要怪誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做過愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我 沒做過啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體明明不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好是因為小學初中一直踢足球的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不踢了 看也知道了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了受傷之外 不踢的理由多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個成不了目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是非常地出色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無意中持續了九年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是感覺到極限了吧 所以熱情就退了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何時開始輸了球也不覺得遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意識中開始退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事很常見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很無聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾乃也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理掉也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我會重畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重畫… 難道你又要報名新人獎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你很喜歡畫漫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你還想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚別想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話要再帶點色情的語調說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚別想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒變嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚很快樂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒快樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐才是 那些捲心菜沒讓仁學長吃下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要問嗎 學弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扔垃圾去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人的關係完全搞不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真早啊 要去打工嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君也辛苦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就沒生氣啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為青山生氣的時候會變成關西腔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒在生氣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那個人真是個奇怪的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美術科對吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名嗎 是啊 她的目標好像成為漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫倒是畫得不錯 就是有點微妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是非常地努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 有種想給她加油的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為聲優 從早上就開始打工 真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多要走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山也好 椎名也好 都找到了能全心投入的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然完全比不上美咲學姐那般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 不知能否有找到的那一日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是亂丟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要道謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看封面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋沒對你說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說在電視和雜誌上至少見到過相貌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為說到椎名真白的話
