Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一回目　毆れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:04.22,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}二回目って　どうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:11.55,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}偶然じゃないよね　三回目が遭うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:15.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}変わった人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:18.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}割と皆いうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:25.76,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}気になったことは 違うんだ　そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:32.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君は多分純粋で　純粋を負けず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:39.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}だから小さな日常にさえ　立ち向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:46.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉じゃ　足りない夢にありが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:50.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}きっとこんな風に始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}新しいトキメキ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:03:01.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉を　知らないふりして行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:05.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}トキメキと夢のありか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第一回 被人毆打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:04.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第二回又會如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:11.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}會有第三回絕對不是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:15.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是個怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:18.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大家好像都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:25.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}應該在意的事不是那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:32.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你或許非常單純 並且不向單純低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:39.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}所以即便是簡單的日常也會抵抗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:46.82,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充滿著夢想的話語便是夢想不足的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:50.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一定是像這樣開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}那片嶄新的心跳世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:03:01.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充滿著夢想的話語 就當作沒有聽過繼續前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:05.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}走向那心跳與夢的所在
