Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:36.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}涙をのみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:39.02,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}不器用だね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:42.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:48.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大空を見上げ何も言えず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:56.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}胸が痛む訳考えていた
